<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="close-adv">close <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kləʊs/    美 /kloʊs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>接近地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As they got closer, they realized that the dog was a wolf.
当他们离得更近时才意识到那不是狗，而是只狼。</p><footer>2017 浙江</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The girl <strong>held</strong> the puppy <strong>close</strong>.
女孩紧紧地抱着小狗。</p></div></div>